<item>
            <title>[LU-7672] Update the script to set up a test Kerberos environment</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7672</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since the Kerberos revival effort is nearly complete, we need to incorporate Kerberos testing into the patch acceptance process making it, at least optional, to test security code changes in Lustre against the existing security test scripts. When Lustre was previously made to work in a Kerberos environment, a script was written to setup the environment needed for Kerberos. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The setup_kerberos script needs to be updated.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
